Share information
Cube Storage Pioneers

Little Robots, Big Business

Since its inception in 1996, AutoStore™ has worked to improve warehouse efficiency. Today, the company’s key value proposition is to deliver an easy-to-use software powered cubic automatic storage and retrieval ecosystem.

The AutoStore solution is modular and flexible, and can automate any warehouse. The system offers a superior customer value proposition across operating metrics, ESG scores, and customer economics.
‍

View video to learn more

entry.title: Grave with the Hands (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that the Grave with the Hands (pictured) commemorates a married couple, divided by society and religion, clasping hands between cemeteries after death?

entry.content: ... that Frank Jonet was appointed as the receiver of the Green Bay Packers from 1933 to 1935, helping to prevent the team from shutting down?

entry.content: ... that Sarah Todd Cunningham was the first woman from the island of Hawaii to serve as a Hawaii territorial senator?

entry.title: Lynn Theatre (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that in 2023, car manufacturer Rivian acquired the historic Lynn Theatre in Laguna Beach, California, and converted it into its first showroom?

entry.content: ... that Max Eisenbud helped make Maria Sharapova the world's highest-paid female athlete for more than a decade?

entry.title: Silvio Hein (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that after Broadway musical composer Silvio Hein died in 1928, the pallbearers at his funeral included Irving Berlin, John Philip Sousa, and Jerome Kern?
